Seriously, you don't have to come.

2
00:00:05,968 --> 00:00:07,563
I'll pick you up tomorrow.

3
00:00:09,633 --> 00:00:10,984
Take a rest for today.

4
00:00:16,969 --> 00:00:18,218
Open the trunk.

5
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:21,656
I know.

6
00:00:25,117 --> 00:00:26,141
I need to hang up now.

7
00:00:28,914 --> 00:00:30,320
You are smoking in the car again.

8
00:00:30,345 --> 00:00:30,884
Okay.

9
00:00:30,909 --> 00:00:31,695
Tomorrow.

10
00:00:42,390 --> 00:00:46,162
(Xiao Lin)

11
00:00:46,195 --> 00:00:48,023
The rain came in so quickly.

12
00:00:49,469 --> 00:00:50,914
How long are you gonna stay this time around?

13
00:00:51,937 --> 00:00:53,023
Three to four days perhaps.

14
00:00:53,546 --> 00:00:55,062
Why don't you stay a little longer?

15
00:00:57,867 --> 00:00:59,750
Did Grandma just call?

16
00:01:00,531 --> 00:01:01,219
Yes.

17
00:01:02,171 --> 00:01:03,086
She knows you're coming back home.

18
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:04,335
And she insists on coming to see you.

19
00:01:05,117 --> 00:01:05,969
I'll pick her up tomorrow.

20
00:01:05,993 --> 00:01:07,265
Is mom home?

21
00:01:11,367 --> 00:01:12,922
Not for now.

22
00:01:12,946 --> 00:01:14,523
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

23
00:01:15,031 --> 00:01:15,875
Yes, I had my meal.

24
00:01:16,547 --> 00:01:17,429
You ate already?

25
00:01:18,273 --> 00:01:19,500
I ate while I was in the shuttle.

26
00:01:28,008 --> 00:01:29,757
Why didn't you bring your girlfriend back?

27
00:01:30,195 --> 00:01:31,000
Huh?

28
00:01:31,024 --> 00:01:31,695
I mean

29
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:34,179
why isn’t your girlfriend coming
with you this time?

30
00:01:35,296 --> 00:01:36,398
We broke up long time ago.

31
00:01:36,422 --> 00:01:37,351
What?

32
00:01:37,375 --> 00:01:38,789
I don't have any feelings for her anymore.

33
00:01:39,265 --> 00:01:41,273
What sort of a relationship did you have with her?

34
00:01:41,297 --> 00:01:43,429
You know your grandmother is still waiting
to see her granddaughter-in-law.

35
00:01:47,922 --> 00:01:50,711
There will be a few of
my friends at home.

36
00:01:50,735 --> 00:01:52,335
Remember to say hello to them.

37
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:54,359
Don't ignore them like you used to do.

38
00:01:55,289 --> 00:01:56,594
You heard me?

39
00:01:56,618 --> 00:01:57,570
Yes, I did.

40
00:02:00,875 --> 00:02:01,867
There you are.

41
00:02:01,892 --> 00:02:03,085
You guys are finally back.

42
00:02:03,110 --> 00:02:04,781
Come and sit.

43
00:02:05,148 --> 00:02:06,320
You guys haven't started drinking yet?

44
00:02:06,345 --> 00:02:07,695
We are waiting for you.

45
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:08,617
You needn't have waited for me.

46
00:02:08,641 --> 00:02:10,562
Let's pour the liquor.

47
00:02:11,156 --> 00:02:12,188
How about the food?

48
00:02:12,212 --> 00:02:13,351
Good.

49
00:02:13,883 --> 00:02:14,711
Let's get some.

50
00:02:16,391 --> 00:02:17,375
Where's your son?

51
00:02:17,867 --> 00:02:18,539
He's back there.

52
00:02:18,563 --> 00:02:19,554
Leave him alone.

53
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,132
Come on.

54
00:02:22,156 --> 00:02:23,140
Let me help you.

55
00:02:23,164 --> 00:02:24,023
You are back, Xiao Lin.

56
00:02:24,477 --> 00:02:25,492
Let's eat together.

57
00:02:25,517 --> 00:02:26,968
I've already eaten. You guys can start without me.

58
00:02:26,992 --> 00:02:27,734
Let me get you a bowl and chopsticks.

59
00:02:27,758 --> 00:02:29,828
No thanks, Auntie.
Please stay seated. I'm full for now.

60
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:31,477
Guess kids don't want to eat with us.

61
00:02:31,906 --> 00:02:34,000
What's tasty when you are surrounded
by a bunch of old men.

62
00:02:34,438 --> 00:02:36,273
Ok, let's drink.

63
00:02:41,233 --> 00:02:42,437
Lin.

64
00:02:42,461 --> 00:02:43,983
Your son is such an obedient child.

65
00:02:44,007 --> 00:02:45,085
Look at my daughter.

66
00:02:45,109 --> 00:02:46,895
I don't even know
if she will go to university.

67
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,764
Right.

68
00:02:47,789 --> 00:02:48,671
I'm worried.

69
00:02:48,696 --> 00:02:49,827
Your daughter is beautiful though.

70
00:02:49,852 --> 00:02:50,741
You have nothing to worry about.

71
00:02:50,765 --> 00:02:53,483
She is a girl. You should see
how beautiful your daughter is.

72
00:02:53,507 --> 00:02:54,233
Is she a flower vase?

73
00:02:54,258 --> 00:02:55,708
She will definitely mend her ways after finding
the perfect mother-in-law.

74
00:02:55,733 --> 00:02:56,928
There is still a chance for her to choose.

75
00:02:56,953 --> 00:02:58,124
Yes.

76
00:02:58,303 --> 00:02:59,139
You just wait to enjoy your life thereafter.

77
00:02:59,164 --> 00:03:00,139
Nevertheless, we're still anxious.

78
00:03:00,164 --> 00:03:01,796
A daughter is a warm jacket.

79
00:03:02,233 --> 00:03:03,694
Look at Wang's son.

80
00:03:03,718 --> 00:03:04,850
He is getting married.

81
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,444
So fast.

82
00:03:06,468 --> 00:03:07,538
When is the wedding?

83
00:03:08,046 --> 00:03:09,483
That brat of mine.

84
00:03:09,507 --> 00:03:10,530
Studying has never been his thing.

85
00:03:10,554 --> 00:03:12,170
However, he managed to
find himself a girlfriend.

86
00:03:12,928 --> 00:03:14,686
Guess it's true when they say
"like father, like son", huh?

87
00:03:15,154 --> 00:03:20,272
Lin, look at your son,
a master of both, pen and sword.

88
00:03:20,296 --> 00:03:21,444
He is cute too.

89
00:03:21,468 --> 00:03:22,733
Oh, forget it.

90
00:03:22,757 --> 00:03:23,655
By the way, have you guys ever noticed?

91
00:03:23,679 --> 00:03:25,397
Liu hasn't gotten married until now.

92
00:03:25,421 --> 00:03:26,413
Which one?

93
00:03:27,155 --> 00:03:28,827
The one we had a drink with last time.

94
00:03:28,851 --> 00:03:29,842
The one who lives next to Wang.

95
00:03:29,866 --> 00:03:31,389
Oh my neighbor.

96
00:03:31,585 --> 00:03:32,866
Yes, the fisherman.

97
00:03:32,891 --> 00:03:34,217
He is in his 40s, right?

98
00:03:34,241 --> 00:03:37,600
I believe there is something seriously wrong
that he is still not married in his 40s.

99
00:03:39,015 --> 00:03:41,460
No matter how many girls
his family made him meet.

100
00:03:41,484 --> 00:03:43,280
Definitely.

101
00:03:43,304 --> 00:03:44,717
There must be something wrong after all.

102
00:03:45,858 --> 00:03:47,928
Either physically or psychologically.

103
00:03:48,506 --> 00:03:49,616
Maybe you are right.

104
00:03:49,827 --> 00:03:52,147
Well, rumor has it that he is gay.

105
00:03:52,171 --> 00:03:54,920
Ok, ok. Stop talking nonsense.

106
00:03:56,054 --> 00:03:56,952
Here we go.

107
00:03:56,977 --> 00:03:58,977
- Let's drink.
- Ok, ok. Let's stop talking about this.

108
00:04:00,538 --> 00:04:02,280
There are so many things happening
in today's society.

109
00:04:03,655 --> 00:04:04,905
Xiao Lin, have some more.

110
00:04:04,929 --> 00:04:06,256
No thanks, you guys dine first.

111
00:04:18,772 --> 00:04:19,780
Xiao Lin.

112
00:04:20,202 --> 00:04:20,741
Huh?

113
00:04:20,765 --> 00:04:21,249
Xiao Lin.

114
00:04:21,274 --> 00:04:22,061
Huh?

115
00:04:22,257 --> 00:04:23,678
Do you have a girlfriend?

116
00:04:24,491 --> 00:04:25,319
Huh?

117
00:04:25,780 --> 00:04:27,256
I said, do you have a girlfriend?

118
00:04:27,890 --> 00:04:29,381
Oh, not yet.

119
00:04:29,405 --> 00:04:32,491
No way. Lin, you should be more concerned.

120
00:04:32,516 --> 00:04:35,280
He is not talking because his Dad is around.

121
00:04:35,304 --> 00:04:36,194
Xiao Lin.

122
00:04:36,554 --> 00:04:38,335
Go get some fruits
for your uncles and aunties.

123
00:04:42,515 --> 00:04:44,351
Is two enough?

124
00:04:45,257 --> 00:04:46,726
It's good.

125
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:47,827
Our main mission is the liquor.

126
00:04:47,851 --> 00:04:48,944
Apples are just decorations on the side.

127
00:04:48,968 --> 00:04:49,670
That's right.

128
00:04:49,694 --> 00:04:52,249
He is being so immature at his age.

129
00:04:52,273 --> 00:04:53,202
It's ok.

130
00:04:53,226 --> 00:04:54,116
Kids are the same.

131
00:04:54,141 --> 00:04:55,600
Let's drink.

132
00:05:07,827 --> 00:05:09,163
Sorry.

133
